2025-07-07.title: Explain Overfitting
2025-07-07.answer: Overfitting is when a model memorizes the training data

2025-07-07.title: What is Supervised Learning?
2025-07-07.answer: Training a model using labeled data

2025-07-08.title: Define Accuracy and Precision
2025-07-08.answer: Accuracy is total correct predictions; Precision is correct positive predictions
